<template>
<el-radio-group v-model="labelPosition" size="small">
  <el-radio-button label="left">左对齐</el-radio-button>
  <el-radio-button label="right">右对齐</el-radio-button>
  <el-radio-button label="top">顶部对齐</el-radio-button>
</el-radio-group>

</template>


<script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        labelPosition: 'left',
        formLabelAlign: {
          name: '',
          region: '',
          type: ''
        }
      };
    }
  }
</script>
